; Performance: 0023_mod_i32
; Why hard: Smoke baseline for signed remainder. Failures here usually indicate broken lowering shared by every later fixture.
; Reveals: mod_i32 lowering to srem
; If LLVM regresses: Uses urem or div without rem; wrong sign on negative inputs.
(core-module
  (core-version 1)
  (decls
    (fn main
      (params)
      (returns i32)
      (do
        (return
          (mod_i32
            (const_i32 42)
            (const_i32 10)
          ) ;; mod_i32
        ) ;; return
      ) ;; do
    ) ;; fn
  ) ;; decls
) ;; core-module
